      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "calendar",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The calendar to use for the computation. "
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "at",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "A reference to an absolute time. On input, points to the absolute time to which components are to be added; on output, points to the result of the computation."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "options",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Options for the calculation. For valid values, see "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/cfcalendar#1667557"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "componentDesc",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "A string that describes the components provided in the vararg parameters. "
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "...",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Vararg parameters giving amounts of each calendrical component in the order specified by "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "componentDesc"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ". The amounts to add may be negative, zero, positive, or any combination thereof."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return_value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "TRUE"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "—and in "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "at"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " the computed time—if "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "at"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " falls inside the defined range of the calendar and it is possible to calculate the absolute time when the components (the calendrical components specified by "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "componentDesc"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and given in the varargs) are added to the input absolute time "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "at"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "; otherwise "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "FALSE"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Some operations can be ambiguous, and the behavior of the computation is calendar-specific, but generally components are added in the order specified."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you specify a “wrap” option ("
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/1533520-component_wrapping_options/kcfcalendarcomponentswrap"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "), the specified components should be incremented and wrap around to zero/one on overflow, but should not cause higher units to be incremented. When “Wrap” is false, overflow in a unit carries into the higher units, as in typical addition. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Note that some computations can take a relatively long time to perform."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The following example shows how to add 2 months and 3 days to absolute time "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "at"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "‘s current value using an existing calendar ("
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "gregorian"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "):"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeListing",
          "code": [
            "CFCalendarAddComponents(gregorian, &at, 0, \"Md\",  2, 3);"
          ],
          "syntax": "occ",
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "2556079",
            "title": "Listing 1"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
